# Frontend Design System

- Read `packages/design-system/README.md` and `TESTING.md` before changing shared primitives or tokens.
- Keep app-specific workflows, data fetching, routing, and product copy out of `packages/design-system`.
- Prefer CSS tokens and existing primitive variants over one-off colors, spacing, or typography.
- Preserve native semantics, keyboard access, labels, and disabled states.
- Only promote UI from `apps/frontend` after it is stable and reusable.
- Run design-system typecheck and affected frontend checks when practical.
